About ISAAC Modules Parent

The Maven Parent POM file for all known ISAAC modules. Declares shared dependencies, sets up the build.

Project Modules

This project has declared the following modules:

Name Description
ISAAC App Interfaces ISAAC Application Interfaces. Modules implement these to provide a compatible module to the isaac-app.
ISAAC JavaFX GUI Utilities Reusable JavaFX Utility Code
ISAAC OTF Utilities Utility code for accessing OTF APIs
ISAAC Data Model ISAAC Data Model classes
ISAAC Importer/Exporter ISAAC Importer and Exporter tooling
ISAAC Content Request Submission Module ISAAC handling for USCRS and LOINC content submission integration.
ISAAC Classifier ISAAC Classifier Module
ISAAC Taxonomy View A Taxonomy GUI implementation for ISAAC
ISAAC LEGO View ISAAC LEGO tooling
ISAAC Search View A Search GUI implementation for ISAAC
ISAAC Application ISAAC GUI - contains application window and menus.
ISAAC Workflow ISAAC Workflow Tooling
ISAAC Info Model View An Info Model View that displays data-model specific refsets
ISAAC List View A List / Batch view implementation for ISAAC
ISAAC Maven Mojo Utilities The Maven Parent POM file for all known ISAAC modules. Declares shared dependencies, sets up the build.
ISAAC Refex Panel A Refex panel implementation for ISAAC
ISAAC New Concept Panel A New Concept panel implementation for ISAAC
ISAAC Constants ISAAC Constants - contains various ConceptSpec style constants for use within ISAAC related tooling.
ISAAC Extensions for DROOLS The Maven Parent POM file for all known ISAAC modules. Declares shared dependencies, sets up the build.
ISAAC Sync Service - GUI Integration ISAAC Profile Sync service, GUI integration for ISAAC
ISAAC Sync Service - GIT implementation ISAAC Profile Sync service, implemented with GIT
ISAAC Sync Service - SVN implementation ISAAC Profile Sync service, implemented with SVN
